; mml2vgm Browser IDE - Chord Progression Sample
; Demonstrates chord playing with multiple parts

@OPNA

; Part 0: Melody
@0 v100 l4 o4
  c e g a2. >c e g a2.

; Part 1: Chords (using tie for sustained notes)
@1 v80 l2 o3
  c~g~e~ c~g~e~ f~a~c~ f~a~c~

; Part 2: Bass
@2 v90 l4 o2
  c2. g2. f2. c2.

; Part 3: SSG Arpeggio
@3 v70 l8 o4
  c e g c e g c2 c e g c e g c2
